source: hand-authored (issue #371 W1a — sidecar provenance, no live capture)
capture_date: 2026-07-04
shape: raw `gh issue list --json number,title,labels,comments` object array
  (pre-transform) — the stub applies the leaf's own jq normalization, so this
  fixture matches the RAW GitHub REST shape itp_github_list_by_state /
  itp_github_count_by_state / itp_github_list_forbidden_combos expect, not
  the normalized {number,title,labels,comments} output.
notes: two entries deliberately out-of-order by number (5 before 3) to
  exercise the leaf's `sort_by(.number)` canonical-sort assertion; #5 carries
  `in-progress` (a transitional label) and #3 carries `approved` (a terminal
  label) so the same fixture also serves itp_list_forbidden_combos.
